    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/21014/pexels-photo.jpg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="person holding a map in a car">
  </div>

  <div class="about-us text-center text-md-right d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center">
    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/11456549/pexels-photo-11456549.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="a blue mercedes">
    <p class="text-center px-4">Become a host and rent your car out</p>
  </div>
</div>
